orbit.com/modules/news/tools.php?tool=print&amp;id=1189500\">Stratton Leopold to Advisory Board</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hypebot.com/hypebot/2009/06/uplaya-cuts-multitiered-alliance-with-the-orchard.html\">Music Intelligence Solutions Partners with The Orchard</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/pressRelease/idUS55195+16-Jun-2008+MW20080616\">Music Intelligence Solutions Partners with The Sync Agency</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S6jg70weJWs\">NBC Network News Feature on uPlaya</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VFuA0MqP8kA\">BBC News Report</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TJL88mBif6U\">Episode of \"Numb3rs\" Inspired by Hit Song Science</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://uplaya.com/about_hss/hssquotes\">Ben Novak's debut single enters the UK Top 40 chart at number 12</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP l